39:01.730 --> 39:06.039
♪ Start from here

39:07.214 --> 39:08.171
- You wanted to see me?

39:08.215 --> 39:10.304
- This is my OR.

39:10.348 --> 39:12.262
Everything I do here
is for a reason.

39:12.306 --> 39:14.177
It works for me.

39:14.221 --> 39:16.354
Now out there on the floor is
a loving, peaceful democracy,

39:16.397 --> 39:18.051
but in there,
it's full-blown dictatorship.

39:18.094 --> 39:19.444
You got it?

39:19.487 --> 39:22.011
- Understood.
- I didn't say you can go.

39:30.368 --> 39:32.152
Run down
the McCarthy technique.

39:32.195 --> 39:35.155
Top to bottom.

39:35.198 --> 39:37.026
- Yes, sir.

39:37.070 --> 39:39.202
You start by opening
the LV apex

39:39.246 --> 39:41.466
at least 1.5cm
from the LAD.

39:41.509 --> 39:43.337
Then,
using a purse string suture,

39:43.381 --> 39:46.122
you pull together the damaged
left ventricular wall.

39:46.775 --> 39:48.734
- Hi.
- We need to talk right now.

39:48.777 --> 39:51.084
- I see you heard about
our plan to sue the city

39:51.127 --> 39:52.346
over lead contamination.

39:52.390 --> 39:53.391
- What? No.

39:53.434 --> 39:54.392
What?

39:54.435 --> 39:56.219
- Oh, then, never mind.

39:56.263 --> 39:57.438
- I'm here because I heard
about your little plan

39:57.482 --> 39:59.048
with the barber.

39:59.092 --> 40:00.093
- Oh, yeah.
Pretty cool, right?

40:00.136 --> 40:02.182
- No, no, not cool.
- Not cool?

40:02.225 --> 40:04.227
No, I'm just training
a barber at Kenny's Kuts

40:04.271 --> 40:07.100
to check his customer's
blood pressure.

40:07.143 --> 40:09.102
- That's it?
- Yeah.

40:09.145 --> 40:11.757
Mostly.
Here me out.

40:11.800 --> 40:13.323
Kenny sees people once a week

40:13.367 --> 40:15.413
in a relaxed
and trusted environment.

40:15.456 --> 40:17.371
You couldn't ask for a better
monitoring situation,

40:17.415 --> 40:21.201
and if anyone exceeds
140/90 for over four weeks...

40:21.244 --> 40:24.030
- The barber
is diagnosing hypertension

40:24.073 --> 40:26.249
and dispensing
prescription meds?

40:26.293 --> 40:27.512
- With my oversight.

40:27.555 --> 40:28.513
- What oversight?
You're not there.

40:28.556 --> 40:30.123
You're here.

40:30.166 --> 40:32.081
- Kenny has a detailed
checklist to follow.

40:32.125 --> 40:35.302
- So do Legos, but no one's
life depends on them.

40:35.345 --> 40:37.260
I mean,
what if mistakes are made?

40:37.304 --> 40:40.394
- There's a built-in system
of checks and balances

40:40.438 --> 40:42.309
that I'll be carefully
supervising,

40:42.352 --> 40:43.571
and, sure, there's some risk,

40:43.615 --> 40:45.486
but Kenny and the others
will be saving lives.

40:45.530 --> 40:47.401
Just imagine--
- Wait, wait, stop.

40:47.445 --> 40:49.229
What others?
You said others?

40:49.272 --> 40:51.144
- Yeah. So far I've enlisted
seven barber shops,

40:51.187 --> 40:53.538
and I'm trying for more.

40:53.581 --> 40:56.236
- Max, what you're doing
is decentralizing

40:56.279 --> 40:58.412
and de-professionalizing
healthcare.

40:58.456 --> 40:59.848
- Exactly.

40:59.892 --> 41:01.415
There's no reason
that healthcare

41:01.459 --> 41:03.286
has to be delivered
in a hospital.

41:03.330 --> 41:05.158
In fact, patients are best
served in an environment

41:05.201 --> 41:06.551
where they're made comfortable

41:06.594 --> 41:09.075
by trusted members
of their own community.

41:09.118 --> 41:12.557
Hospitals have to go
meet patients where they live,

41:12.600 --> 41:14.297
not the other way around.

41:14.341 --> 41:16.561
- So in your idealized world,

41:16.604 --> 41:19.346
